bioconda.name: bioconductor-swath2stats
bioconda.summary: Transform and Filter SWATH Data for Statistical Packages

biotools.summary: This package is intended to transform SWATH data from the OpenSWATH software into a format readable by other statistics packages while performing filtering, annotation and FDR estimation.
